original_title: Day In The Life of The #1 BBQ In Texas
overview: Hundreds of pounds of brisket, ribs, sausages, and turkey are smoked at this somewhat hidden spot in Kennedale, Texas. Long lines start piling up 5 hours before the place even opens. People come from all across the country just to try their food, especially their house-baked bread (which is unheard of in Texas).
tagline: Day In The Life of The #1 BBQ In Texas
title: Day In The Life of The #1 BBQ In Texas
